{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved learning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember saying to my mother, I will never learn how to read.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I did enjoy reading tremendously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Poland, the libraries were not free, and you had to pay for checking out books.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to do this continually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I enjoyed that very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a lot of books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my favorite gift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody knew that I enjoyed getting books as gifts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember by Johanna Spyri.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that stands out very much in my mind, because I kind of wished I had been Heidi and had that experience.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember reading James Fenimore Cooper, you know, I couldn't imagine what it was like to be a Native American, or an Indian in those days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Adventures, Western stories, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember particularly, at the beginning-- you know, just prior to the war, and at the beginning of the war, there was a heightened feeling of something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people used to congregate in the courtyard of the apartment building and talk about war, and feeling that if something-- if things were going to happen, things weren't going to be so good for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as a child, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think that I felt any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really wouldn't have known what that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember everybody talking, congregating, and-- and speaking about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a feeling of not understanding what was happening, but feeling that something was ominous, because everybody was concerned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the older people were concerned and talked in hushed tones, and listened to the foreign broadcasts on the Telefunken radio-- on the shortwave.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- it just-- a fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
